## CLI reference

    toroidzip encode [flags] <input.f64> <output.tzrz>
    toroidzip decode <input.tzrz> <output.f64>
    toroidzip analyze <input.f64>

    --entropy-mode raw|lossless|quantized  (default lossless)
    --sig-figs N       significant decimal figures 1–9 (implies quantized)
    --precision N      precision bits 1–30 (implies quantized)
    --auto             auto-select mode from data analysis
    --lossy            shorthand for --entropy-mode quantized
    --drift-mode A|B   A=reanchor (default), B=Kahan compensate
    --reanchor-interval N  (default 256)

